的任务是引来一发灭绝令才可以回家，你有什么办法完成这个任务？ 你只是一个普通人——没有灵能、没有特殊知识、没有资源、没有权力，你甚至可能是个文盲。 生活在巢都底层、农业世界或前线战壕里。 但你的目标是引来一发灭绝令，而且必须确保帝国无法用常规手段镇压你（比如派星界军平叛、阿斯塔特斩首、审判庭净化）。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-459c5ad0df98e58830b026aea6cad7e7_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1940537812249191616"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIqN3Zp4TVjZZ1EAMaCTExNjI0NjM5MyCLyYfFBjAAODNAGnITMTk0MDUzNzgxMjI0OTE5MTYxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1776566616.447476", "card_id": "Q_1974182601813140181", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "三峡水库淤满了以后会怎么处理？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d48c8641bc777e70edd2428bb5fd3792_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1974182601813140181"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIqN3Zp4TVjZZ1EAMaCTExNzM4MjY1MiCylfHIBjAAOIYBQBtyEzE5NzQxODI2MDE4MTMxNDAxODF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1776566616.447776", "card_id": "Q_2028573090301395743", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 250}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "请问 3500 的工资，买什么车合适哦？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "求解答"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ab9f88eff352f54da8247836e2df1e47_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2028573090301395743"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIqN3Zp4TVjZZ1EAMaCTExOTE